---
title: SuperQuick Scallion Turkey Noodles with Sesame and Garlic
description: This savoury and flavourful dish features chow mein noodles tossed with tender turkey and crisp sugar snap peas. Hoisin and soy sauce add richness and an umami depth to each bite. Quick to prepare and satisfying, this recipe is perfect for a delicious weeknight meal.

